{"tid":860731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★曾俊華：料八成工種未來20年內消失","createTime":"2018-10-13T14:27:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T16:13:02.000Z","uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bbb26031a66eac3ea2b619098c6e4406e9f73771","tid":860731,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T14:27:54.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】前財政司司長曾俊華指科技發展已超乎學校教育能力，但本港的教育制度卻仍沿用工業時代的藍圖，認為有需要改革。<br />\n<br />\n曾俊華今日出席論壇致辭時，講述他對21世紀教育的看法。他預期隨著科技發展，七至八成現有工種未來20年或會逐漸消失，而學生難以像以往般，在人生的中頭20年學畢足以應付一生需要的知識。<br />\n<br />\n曾俊華批評現今的教育方法不合時宜，令學生得不到適當的工具、知識甚至思維去應付未來遇到的新問題，削弱競爭力。<br />\n<br />\n曾俊華建議更理性分配智識，在不同成長階段適時吸收，教育制度也要改革，學生需要學習全新知識、技術、工作模式，甚至價值觀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%96%99%E5%85%AB%E6%88%90%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%AE%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%8620%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A7%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1-%E6%9B%BE%E4%BF%8A%E8%8F%AF%E4%BF%83%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6-045200546.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2596%2599%25E5%2585%25AB%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E6%259C%25AA%25E4%25BE%258620%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%25B6%2588%25E5%25A4%25B1-%25E6%259B%25BE%25E4%25BF%258A%25E8%258F%25AF%25E4%25BF%2583%25E6%2594%25B9%25E9%259D%25A9%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%25BA%25A6-045200546.html&d=Dr3og%2FehezBAl2htW82PDC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=805a3023\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%96%99%E5%85%AB%E6%88%90%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%AE%E6%9C%AA%E4%BE%8620%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A7%E6%B6%88%E5%A4%B1-%E6%9B%BE%E4%BF%8A%E8%8F%AF%E4%BF%83%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%88%B6%E5%BA%A6-045200546.html</a>"},{"pid":"3346eb0d6a11bf2707a43aac36302989422d0793","tid":860731,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T14:28:07.000Z","msg":"Apple store<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa9011cb4f74226445bd7d323e06c1c306997ff","tid":860731,"uid":560